  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">RF - Nibulon WC Loan</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project was approved in the context of the Bank&apos;s response to the COVID-19  pandemic. To avoid delays to the delivery of this project, the Bank&apos;s President  granted a deviation from the ordinary timelines for PSD disclosure, as  contemplated by Section V of the Directive on Access to Information. Details of  the Bank&apos;s response to COVID-19, and this deviation, can be found on the Bank&apos;s  website.  A senior secured loan of up to USD 27 million (the &quot;loan&quot;) to Nibulon LLC  (the &quot;borrower&quot;) under the Resilience Framework. The loan will enable Nibulon  LLC to secure sufficient working capital financing for the following seasons  and support in further developing its trading activity in Ukraine amid the  adverse impact of COVID-19 on its business.</narrative>
  </description>
